        </div>
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-retro mb-8">
          Bridging <span class="text-neon animate-neon-pulse">Digital</span> and 
          <span class="text-secondary animate-flicker">Physical</span> Worlds
